                  ‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ó‡∏ò‡∏¥‡πå‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡∏î‡∏π‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏ñ‡∏π‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡∏Å‡∏ñ‡∏≠‡∏ô‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢ Super Admin
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
                <strong>Super Admin:</strong> ${userEmail}<br>
                <strong>‡∏ß‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà:</strong> ${new Date().toLocaleString('th-TH')}
              </p>
              
              <div style="background: #f0f7ff; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #1e40af;">
                  <strong>‚ÑπÔ∏è ‡∏´‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏ï‡∏∏:</strong> ‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏á‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ñ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏ê‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏∞‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏±‡πà‡∏ß‡πÑ‡∏õ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏õ‡∏Å‡∏ï‡∏¥
                </p>
              </div>
              
              ${webAppUrl ? `
                <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                  <a href="${webAppUrl}" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 15px 40px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 25px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);">
                    üîó ‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏™‡∏π‡πà‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö
                  </a>
                </div>
                
                <p style="color: #999; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
                  ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏±‡∏î‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏¥‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ:<br>
                  <code style="background: #f0f0f0; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 5px; color: #667eea;">${webAppUrl}</code>
                </p>
              ` : ''}
              
              <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 30px 0;">
              
              <p style="color: #999; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin: 0;">
                ‡∏´‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏™‡∏á‡∏™‡∏±‡∏¢ ‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏≤‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠ Super Admin<br>
                <strong>‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏°‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö</strong>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
